  "detailed_description": "Weggye's Adventures throws you into the magical world of the little plant named Weggye.<br />\r\nBut an evil tree wants to turn the whole world into a wasteland.<br />\r\nTo do this, he hunts all empowering creatures. Sunny was locked in a cage.<br />\r\nThe Baninos hide in fear. And to protect itself, the tree has its energy<br />\r\ncaptured in crystals. Can you help Weggye to save the world.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nFeatures:<br />\r\n<br />\r\n● Find keys in chests to free Sunny.<br />\r\n● Explore the landscape to find the hiding Baninos.<br />\r\n● Collect crystals<br />\r\n● Collect gold nuggets to get life.<br />\r\n● Fight a variety of monsters using different skills.<br />\r\n● But be careful! Evil does not sleep.",
  "about_the_game": "Weggye's Adventures throws you into the magical world of the little plant named Weggye.<br />\r\nBut an evil tree wants to turn the whole world into a wasteland.<br />\r\nTo do this, he hunts all empowering creatures. Sunny was locked in a cage.<br />\r\nThe Baninos hide in fear. And to protect itself, the tree has its energy<br />\r\ncaptured in crystals. Can you help Weggye to save the world.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nFeatures:<br />\r\n<br />\r\n● Find keys in chests to free Sunny.<br />\r\n● Explore the landscape to find the hiding Baninos.<br />\r\n● Collect crystals<br />\r\n● Collect gold nuggets to get life.<br />\r\n● Fight a variety of monsters using different skills.<br />\r\n● But be careful! Evil does not sleep.",
